  m_Name: WodeWoDeath
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: KyndeBlade.Core::KyndeBlade.StoryBeat
  BeatId: WodeWoDeath
  Text: "Pale hands reach from the gloaming. The fae take him\u2014not gently. They
    pull him apart, root from branch from breath, as if he were nothing. His voice
    breaks. \"Dreamer... I tried my best... to...\" Cold fingers close. What remains
    is scattered. The forest weeps. He does not rise again."
  SpeakerName: Narrator
